      "rationale": "All three FEA platforms (FDA in-house, Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1, DePuy Synthes internal solver) maintain formal SQA programs. Release notes, verification test results, and change-control records are available. Input files are stored under version control with audit trail. Gradation 2 requirement satisfied."
